# Output directories — selective carve-out for committed audit artifacts.
# Anchored to repo root so source-layer dirs (src/screener/data/) are NOT
# ignored. Universe Parquet snapshots and per-ticker splits ledgers ARE
# committed (small, audit-relevant); per-ticker prices.parquet stays local.
# Phase 1 originally said `/data/`; Phase 2 (D-19 reconciled with D-06 per
# Amendment 2026-05-02) carves out two committed paths.
/data/*
!/data/universe/
!/data/universe/.gitkeep
!/data/universe/*.parquet
!/data/ohlcv/
/data/ohlcv/**/prices.parquet
!/data/ohlcv/**/splits.parquet
!/data/ohlcv/**/.gitkeep
!/data/snapshots/
/data/snapshots/*.parquet
!/data/snapshots/.gitkeep

# Phase 8 (OPS-05 / D-04 / D-11): observability artifacts.
# data/runs.jsonl — relocated from /runs.jsonl per D-04 (was repo-root).
# data/heartbeat.txt — weekly heartbeat per D-11 (defeats 60-day idle disable).
# Both files are committed; the auto-commit action's file_pattern in
# refresh.yml + heartbeat.yml relies on these carve-outs to pass git add.
!/data/runs.jsonl
!/data/heartbeat.txt

# Phase 8 (OPS-02 fix / Pitfall #4): reports/<date>.md MUST be committable
# past the blanket /reports/ ignore. Mirror the data/universe/ carve-out
# idiom. Without these two carve-outs the OPS-02 auto-commit silently no-ops.
!/reports/
!/reports/*.md

# Phase 6 — fundamentals + insider + pattern audit (gitignored per D-05).
# Literal blanket-ignore lines so the Wave 0 verifier finds the expected
# `^data/<dir>/$` patterns. Anchor each directory with a committed
# `.gitkeep` so the runtime dir exists even when contents are absent
# (mirrors the Phase 2 snapshots carve-out).
data/fundamentals/
data/insider/
data/pattern_audit/
!/data/fundamentals/
/data/fundamentals/*
!/data/fundamentals/.gitkeep
!/data/insider/
/data/insider/*
!/data/insider/.gitkeep
!/data/pattern_audit/
/data/pattern_audit/*
!/data/pattern_audit/.gitkeep

# Phase 7 (RESEARCH A4 — paper-trade history IS the v1.x performance contract;
# commit the SQLite file, mirror the splits.parquet allowlist idiom).
!/data/journal.sqlite

